// Function to check if parameter is odd


Complete the function to check whether the parameter to the function is odd.
The function should accept an integer parameter i.
For odd parameter return 1 else return 0.
/*
 * The isOdd function returns 1 if input parameter is odd, Otherwise it returns 0
 * The function should accept an integer parameter i
 */
int isOdd(int i)
{

/* Write Code to return whether the parameter i is odd here */

if(i%2==0)
{
return 0;
}
else return 1;


}
